('fb4ab987-c455-4034-adf1-ec6cecb3aeac'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Chicharron Green Sauce', 'For shoppers who care about flavour as much as function, Chicharron Green Sauce offers bright green-chile freshness and a mouth-watering tang for solo snacking and afternoon cravings. Chicharron Green Sauce delivers its reward in two steps: texture first, then bright green-chile freshness and a mouth-watering tang, a combination that suits solo snacking and afternoon cravings. Light, crunchy chicharrón coated in zesty green salsa flavour; a useful detail when planning a more adventurous pantry. The strongest serving ideas for Chicharron Green Sauce are solo snacking and afternoon cravings; sharing with friends and family; and hot sauce and lime, covering both quick cravings and planned menus. Chicharron Green Sauce is a practical match for a more adventurous pantry because its role in solo snacking and afternoon cravings is immediately clear. Corner Mex stocks Chicharron Green Sauce for shoppers in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and the wider UAE.'),
