('11172dc7-eeaa-4657-8da8-1d5e2a25c154'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Huitlacoche, La Costeña', 'For shoppers who care about flavour as much as function, Huitlacoche, La Costeña offers a deep, savoury umami character and an earthy, woodland-like depth for tacos. Reach for Huitlacoche, La Costeña when serving tacos; quesadillas and melted-cheese dishes; and soups, stews and broths; it adds interest without making the occasion complicated. Earthy, bold, and rich in umami, Huitlacoche (Mexican truffle) is a delicacy straight from the cornfields of Mexico; a product cue that sets expectations for tacos. For a family-style table, Huitlacoche, La Costeña feels considered without becoming difficult to enjoy or serve. Huitlacoche, La Costeña gives cooks a clear direction for tacos: build the dish around a deep, savoury umami character and an earthy, woodland-like depth rather than seasoning by guesswork. The 380g presentation of Huitlacoche, La Costeña makes the portion easy to plan for a family-style table. Huitlacoche, La Costeña is available online from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
