('2e339671-0295-49a4-a7a9-8f606aced012'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex', 'Choose Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex for a creamy, savoury bean profile and the mellow sweetness of corn when planning layered tostadas. In the kitchen, Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex earns its place with layered tostadas; dips, nachos and sharing boards; and sharing with friends and family, where its character stays easy to recognise. Intermex Golden Tostadas are lightly toasted corn discs made the authentic Mexican way, golden, crispy, and made to be topped; a detail that explains its role in layered tostadas. Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex is a practical match for a quick weekday meal because its role in layered tostadas is immediately clear. Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex works as a flexible base for layered tostadas; a creamy, savoury bean profile and the mellow sweetness of corn leaves room for the cook to shape the final plate. The 10 pieces presentation of Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex makes the portion easy to plan for a quick weekday meal. The product information supplied for Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex also notes: gluten-free. Corner Mex stocks Golden Tostadas 10 pieces, Intermex for shoppers in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and the wider UAE.'),
