('40d1f547-99c9-4441-a1be-1d5b773516af'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración', 'The appeal of Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración lies in bright green-chile freshness and a lingering smoky depth, especially in seafood, ceviche and fish tacos. Use Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración with seafood, ceviche and fish tacos; marinades and spice pastes; and grilled meats and vegetables to add a more deliberate Mexican note to the plate. A refreshingly bold twist on salsa, Salsa Mojito Verde by La Conspiración combines roasted chiles with fresh spearmint for a zesty, herbaceous kick; a detail that explains its role in seafood, ceviche and fish tacos. For a quick weekday meal, Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración feels considered without becoming difficult to enjoy or serve. Because Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración expresses bright green-chile freshness and a lingering smoky depth clearly, a small amount can redirect seafood, ceviche and fish tacos with purpose. The 250 g presentation of Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración makes the portion easy to plan for a quick weekday meal. Mojito Green Sauce, La Conspiración is available online from Corner Mex for delivery in Dubai, Abu Dhabi and across the UAE.'),
