('3660cf57-5561-415c-8fc9-96652ec24441'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label)', 'Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label) brings the more intense heat of Valentina''s black label and Valentina''s tangy chile character to a Mexican hot sauce made for more expressive food moments. The strongest serving ideas for Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label) are micheladas; cocktails and savoury drinks; and tacos, covering both quick cravings and planned menus. Mexico’s cult-favorite hot sauce, now in its extra-hot black-label version; a useful detail when planning a more adventurous pantry. Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label) works especially well for a more adventurous pantry, particularly when the plan includes micheladas. The reason to choose Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label) is practical as well as emotional: it gives micheladas more character without demanding a complicated recipe. The 370 ml presentation of Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label) makes the portion easy to plan for a more adventurous pantry. Make Valentina Salsa Picante Very Hot (Black Label) part of the next pantry restock with online UAE delivery from Corner Mex.'),
