('dc81184d-8f9b-4b38-9b04-17c16779e859'::uuid, 'en'::public.lang_code, 'Mazapan Original, De la Rosa', 'Mazapan Original, De la Rosa is a Mexican sweet with a clear point of view: a rounded nutty flavour and a generous, comforting sweetness. In the kitchen, Mazapan Original, De la Rosa earns its place with solo snacking and afternoon cravings; sharing with friends and family; and nostalgic treats and playful gifting, where its character stays easy to recognise. Keep Mazapan Original, De la Rosa in mind for a thoughtful food gift, when the promise of a rounded nutty flavour and a generous, comforting sweetness helps people choose quickly. De la Rosa Mazapán is Mexico’s beloved peanut candy, known for its soft, crumbly texture and rich nutty flavor; a product cue that sets expectations for solo snacking and afternoon cravings. For shoppers curious about a rounded nutty flavour and a generous, comforting sweetness, Mazapan Original, De la Rosa offers a low-friction way to explore it through solo snacking and afternoon cravings. The 336 g presentation of Mazapan Original, De la Rosa makes the portion easy to plan for a thoughtful food gift. Order Mazapan Original, De la Rosa from Corner Mex when planning solo snacking and afternoon cravings, with delivery across the UAE.'),
